{"tid":759653,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雨量更大　颱風更強　旱季更長 暖化加劇　北半球持續高燒","createTime":"2018-07-28T21:28:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T00:41:32.000Z","uid":57677,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"7970b77d37b39aa820c232e63d1afa9eebd7a7fb","tid":759653,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T21:28:11.000Z","msg":"香港前天文台長林超英2008年曾預測「香港2020年將再沒有冬天」，當時聽起來像天方夜譚，10年後的今天已逐步應驗，近月美加、歐洲、俄羅斯以至日本，整個北半球均受熱浪襲擊，香港今年5月亦錄得33℃或以上「15連熱」的紀錄，高溫暖化似乎已成常態。<br />\n高溫乾燥　山火面積增<br />\n<br />\n世界氣象組織前日發聲明，確認北半球暖化速度快於全球水平，並特別關注「五大天氣危害」之一的山火問題。北半球異常炎熱和乾燥的天氣令各地森林更易燃，且火災面積呈增長趨勢；山火釋放大量二氧化碳和毒物，又會加劇全球變暖並形成污染。如此惡性循環下，造成的問題已不止「中暑」、「曬黑」那麼簡單，還影響全球生態、氣候以至人類呼吸道健康，長遠甚至造成糧食短缺及社會動盪。<br />\n美國德州科技大學氣候科學中心總監海霍（Katherine Hayhoe）說：「有天跑道可能熱到融掉，飛機不能起飛，水源亦出現短缺。」國家海洋及大氣管理局氣象研究學家赫寧（Martin Hoerling）就指出暖化將引致極端氣候，「雨量更大、颱風更強、旱季更長」"},{"pid":"27333546a996fdb8e65d17f49e094c3386f507dd","tid":759653,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T21:28:44.000Z","msg":"areustupid"},{"pid":"10745f683131c2ee2b2fbe17589de38470ac62c3","tid":759653,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T21:29:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180729/20463254\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463254&d=edoxUIiW2rOnmaHAoo5pHCwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=edb88cfa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180729%2F20463254&h=ec6774fc\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180729/20463254</a>"},{"pid":"e0dd5bfaa68f59090eb6aa1552cda0ae8245d33e","tid":759653,"uid":31990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:28:10.000Z","msg":"北半球最大污染源係咪強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以北半球寧捨暖化得快？"},{"pid":"05cdc205fcf596745ccf86b810771f99f3e4b500","tid":759653,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:34:41.000Z","msg":"夏天特別熱=無冬天？？"},{"pid":"b2f5f15b55e8951c89c2022a7b21a72a84286bd9","tid":759653,"uid":188310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05cdc205fcf596745ccf86b810771f99f3e4b500","tid":759653,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:34:41.000Z","msg":"夏天特別熱=無冬天？？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T23:59:12.000Z","msg":"熱到去冬天"},{"pid":"258e25cd1c29a23412792045ecc11e28813302c6","tid":759653,"uid":109602,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T00:00:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b63b3bb2001a8e80525693572cf52715fb12cbec","tid":759653,"uid":96146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T00:11:06.000Z","msg":"Hannover前日真係熱到機場跑道變形 搞到成晚所有機都冇得飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"948b0e696a4a276f407eb71ef731b378ab86f1e6","tid":759653,"uid":132038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T00:22:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2141a13a659000dd22e9485185568f60f424019e","tid":759653,"uid":164050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T00:24:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8c5a8bf9db672417dad8dda20707d9db3f723cc","tid":759653,"uid":21392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T00:25:44.000Z","msg":"最怕唔係熱<br />\n係一熱就有昆蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa65d439c1506a8c85d4012e40160e5948c3ec9a","tid":759653,"uid":54812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T00:41:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>北半球最大污染源係咪強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.g